title: More (Girl You Think You Know)*
lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet:
[Verse]
I'm a girl and I'm a lover, not always very smart
I'm a pessimist, a hypocrite with a telltale heart
But I work hard, and I'm kind
Got a forest fire mind on most days
I'm a little insecure, I'm a little too honest
I care way too much about getting into college
And right now I'm a mess, things don't make sense
But they will soon
[Chorus]
I am more
Than I could ever show
I am more
Than the girl you think you know
And I know
